	(gr_text "QA test fixture, GitLab issue #24525 ({dblquote}DRC ignores Barcodes, Tables and Images in Edge.Cuts{dblquote})\n\nThe text, dimension, table and barcode placed on the Edge.Cuts layer are\nINTENTIONAL. Each must raise a {dblquote}Text or graphic on Edge.Cuts layer{dblquote} DRC\nviolation, because each of those item types plots geometry onto the board\noutline and would corrupt the fabricated edge.\n\nThe reference image on Edge.Cuts is ALSO intentional and must NOT raise a\nviolation, because reference images are never plotted to any output.\n\nDo not {dblquote}fix{dblquote} or clean up this board. The expected result is 4 violations\n(text, dimension, table, barcode) and 0 from the image."
		(at 100 68 0)
